Class ObjectField

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.psddev.dari.db.Record
      • com.psddev.dari.db.ObjectField
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Recordable, HtmlObject, Cloneable, Comparable<Record>

    @Recordable.Embedded
public class ObjectField
extends Record
    Description of how field values can be stored in a state.
